Proof of concept of the following things working together:

- cucumber-jvm
- cucumber-scala
- spring
- scala-spring

Gotchas:

- add this repository to spring.xml (for scala-spring)

		<repositories>
	   		<repository>
				<id>milestone.repo.springsource.org</id>
				<name>repo.springsource.org-milestone</name>
				<url>https://repo.springsource.org/libs-milestone</url>
			</repository>
		</repositories>

To run:
- mvn package && ./run_tests.sh
